com.hazelcast.internal.nearcache.impl.invalidation

Class MetaDataGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.internal.nearcache.impl.invalidation.MetaDataGenerator

  • public class MetaDataGenerator
extends Object
    Responsible for partition-sequence and partition UUID generation. Used by invalidator to generate metadata for invalidation events.

    This metadata is used by RepairingHandler and RepairingTask to act against possible invalidation-miss and partition-loss.

    One instance per service is created. Used on member side.
